                              @{u}What the hell is it?@{uu}


      Hi!   Welcome  in  guide to may new very simply, shortly, easy & more more
others  pretty  words  for  greetz my job!  :) I was written this program when I
very  many  time  used  Internet's  programms...   This  util  counted seconds &
minutes,  after hours :) when I surffed on www, ftp and IRC!  :) So...  it's all
for this part guide!

      Sorry  for  my  ugly  english,  but  in  my  school englis not prefered /I
finished all schools many years ago :)/ :(.

      Program  /???/ was written in AmigaE.  It's in 100% user & system friendly
and has status full Public Domain and MailWare!  :)

      It's all!  Have a nice fun with Stopper!

@{u}                                                                                @{uu}
