@NODE "System" "Stopper.guide/System"
@PREV "WhatIs"
@NEXT "Instal"
@{u}                                                                                @{uu}

@{b}
                               ╗ SÀTÀOÀPÀPÀEÀR ½
@{ub}
                      @{u}Which computers can Stopper run on?@{uu}

     This simply program runs on all Amiga with OS2.0+. I tested it on:

-> A1200/2MBChip
-> A1200/2MBChip/4MBFast
-> A1200/2MBChip/8MBFast/Blizzard1230/50MHz
-> A1200/2MBChip/16MBFast/Apollo1240/40MHz

     On this configs all options works good! So... You need too:

-> XenPL.font         -> included
-> reqtools.library   -> included
-> many time to count -> not included

@{u}                                                                                @{uu}
@ENDNODE

